<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQs - Course Management System</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h1>
        <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        How can I submit my request through the system?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Students can use the Course Management System to submit requests for course registration,
                        section changes, or capstone registration directly from the platform. The system will
                        automatically notify the department head about the requests.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                        How will the department head manage the requests?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        The department head will receive notifications of student requests and can take appropriate
                        actions based on the system's recommendations. This helps streamline the process and reduces the
                        need for face-to-face interactions.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>